para_trans: New Roma Care at Kalamnuri, District Hingoli
Regarding sanction as a special case for setting up the unit.
Government Decision No: Establishment-2024 / Q.64 / Health-4
Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, Mumbai: Go by No. / Room 3 / TCU / Proposal Arena
Proposal: - The establishment of a new Roma Care Unit at Rural Hospital, Akhara Balapur, Taluka Kalamnuri, District Hingoli was under consideration of the Government.
Government Decision: - New Roma Care Unit at Rural Hospital, Akhara Balapur, Taluka Kalamnuri, District Hingoli
The establishment is being approved as a special case.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
